---
import "../../../styles/animations.css";
---

<section id="faq" class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16 animation-element fade-in-up">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading mb-4 text-primary-900">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-secondary-700">
          Everything you need to know about our financial services
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="space-y-6 stagger-animation">
        <!-- FAQ Item 1 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 animation-element fade-in-up">
          <details class="group">
            <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-medium cursor-pointer list-none">
              <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary-900">What services does Crown provide?</span>
              <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
                <svg fill="none" height="24" shape-rendering="geometricPrecision" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24">
                  <path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path>
                </svg>
              </span>
            </summary>
            <p class="text-secondary-700 mt-3 group-open:animate-fadeIn">
              Crown provides comprehensive financial services for startups and growing businesses, including bookkeeping, accounting, tax preparation, financial reporting, CFO services, and strategic financial planning. We tailor our services to meet the specific needs of your business.
            </p>
          </details>
        </div>
        
        <!-- FAQ Item 2 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 animation-element fade-in-up">
          <details class="group">
            <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-medium cursor-pointer list-none">
              <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary-900">How much do your services cost?</span>
              <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
                <svg fill="none" height="24" shape-rendering="geometricPrecision" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24">
                  <path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path>
                </svg>
              </span>
            </summary>
            <p class="text-secondary-700 mt-3 group-open:animate-fadeIn">
              Our pricing is based on the specific services you need and the complexity of your financial situation. We offer tiered packages starting at $1,000/month for startups, with custom pricing for more complex needs. Schedule a consultation for a personalized quote.
            </p>
          </details>
        </div>
        
        <!-- FAQ Item 3 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 animation-element fade-in-up">
          <details class="group">
            <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-medium cursor-pointer list-none">
              <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary-900">Do you work with early-stage startups?</span>
              <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
                <svg fill="none" height="24" shape-rendering="geometricPrecision" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24">
                  <path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path>
                </svg>
              </span>
            </summary>
            <p class="text-secondary-700 mt-3 group-open:animate-fadeIn">
              Yes! We specialize in working with startups at all stages, from pre-seed to Series B and beyond. Our Startup package is designed specifically for early-stage companies that need professional financial management without the cost of a full-time finance team.
            </p>
          </details>
        </div>
        
        <!-- FAQ Item 4 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 animation-element fade-in-up">
          <details class="group">
            <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-medium cursor-pointer list-none">
              <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary-900">What accounting software do you use?</span>
              <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
                <svg fill="none" height="24" shape-rendering="geometricPrecision" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24">
                  <path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path>
                </svg>
              </span>
            </summary>
            <p class="text-secondary-700 mt-3 group-open:animate-fadeIn">
              We primarily work with QuickBooks Online and Xero, but we're experienced with various financial tools and can adapt to your existing systems. We also integrate with popular tools like Gusto for payroll, Bill.com for bill payment, Expensify for expense management, and more.
            </p>
          </details>
        </div>
        
        <!-- FAQ Item 5 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 animation-element fade-in-up">
          <details class="group">
            <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-medium cursor-pointer list-none">
              <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary-900">How quickly can you get started?</span>
              <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
                <svg fill="none" height="24" shape-rendering="geometricPrecision" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24">
                  <path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path>
                </svg>
              </span>
            </summary>
            <p class="text-secondary-700 mt-3 group-open:animate-fadeIn">
              We can typically begin working with new clients within 1-2 weeks of signing an engagement letter. The onboarding process includes setting up systems, transferring financial data, and establishing reporting processes. For urgent situations, we can often expedite this timeline.
            </p>
          </details>
        </div>
        
        <!-- FAQ Item 6 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 animation-element fade-in-up">
          <details class="group">
            <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-medium cursor-pointer list-none">
              <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary-900">Do you help with fundraising?</span>
              <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
                <svg fill="none" height="24" shape-rendering="geometricPrecision" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24">
                  <path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path>
                </svg>
              </span>
            </summary>
            <p class="text-secondary-700 mt-3 group-open:animate-fadeIn">
              Yes, we provide financial support for fundraising efforts, including creating investor-ready financial models, pitch deck financials, and due diligence preparation. Our CFO services can help you develop a compelling financial narrative for investors and answer tough financial questions during the fundraising process.
            </p>
          </details>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- FAQ CTA -->
      <div class="text-center mt-12 animation-element fade-in-up">
        <p class="text-lg text-secondary-700 mb-4">Still have questions? We're here to help.</p>
        <a href="#contact" class="btn bg-primary-600 hover:bg-primary-700 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-md transition-all">Contact Us</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
  import { initAnimations } from "../../../scripts/animationObserver.js";
  initAnimations();
</script>
